{"tid":1027024,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵站被陌生男指認是女騙徒　女神陳婉衡：唔知佢白撞定有問題","createTime":"2019-02-18T13:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T12:02:07.000Z","uid":12558,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea97639e12f9d8e5d3613f66fcbaf560f2554b2","tid":1027024,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:51:25.000Z","msg":"陳婉衡（Alycia）身為藝人，大家都會以為她見過不少狂蜂浪蝶，但事實上機會少之又少，昨日（15日）終於讓Alycia遇上一單烏龍事，被嚇得驚魂未定的她更將事發經過，放到社交網站與網友分享。<br />\n<br />\nAlycia在Instagram分享指，原定乘搭港鐵去上跳舞堂，突然間有男子上前指她欠錢，更用手機追拍她。Alycia留言說：「無啦啦有位男士走埋嚟話我爭佢錢。全程用手機拍住我，追住我，跟埋我落車都唔肯比我走又話要報警。我好驚諗住搵港鐵職員求助。」<br />\n<br />\n想不到男子更先Alycia一步報警，當警員到場見到該男子與又驚又怕的Alycia都不禁有些混亂，即時將二人分開並帶到港鐵站內的警局，在港鐵職員與警員協助下，以干犯港鐵附例警告並要求該名男子刪除片段，事件才得以解決。<br />\n<br />\nAlycia接受《香港01》訪問，指該男子憑聲線指認她是女騙徒，她無奈表示：「佢話我認得你呀，你係新加坡人嘛，然後講了一個英文名，不是我的名字，當時不知道對方是認錯人、白撞還是有問題，有嘗試與他溝通解釋，但佢係完全唔聽，更拎手機拍住我，仲話報警。」Alycia就指今次事件未致於有損失，不過就嚇到驚魂未定大呻好黑仔，加上糾纏了一段時間而錯過了跳舞堂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fe9wEMJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFe9wEMJ.png&h=330ed4b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wMVG1Z3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMVG1Z3.png&h=1a1ad166&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fvj1hyp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvj1hyp.png&h=92a813f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xA3dS6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxA3dS6K.png&h=694b027d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DsMCAj5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDsMCAj5.png&h=e376272b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JvTmhyr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJvTmhyr.png&h=75c42f5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8833abd39f36be569d2570e59ce2eaf10f210ff5","tid":1027024,"uid":216270,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:52:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebd82cce6df0f8a44ba2c57926756e703a001dad","tid":1027024,"uid":2419,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130614/photo/0614-00176-021b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130614%2Fphoto%2F0614-00176-021b1.jpg&h=9ec70ae2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1e6a1cce379dda5baae0261ed1e3d1f8c963b65","tid":1027024,"uid":15730,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:13:54.000Z","msg":"副計真係不得了"},{"pid":"f95b369dc0d8d6cdb1de4ac3baac179e4713ad5b","tid":1027024,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1e6a1cce379dda5baae0261ed1e3d1f8c963b65","tid":1027024,"uid":15730,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:13:54.000Z","msg":"副計真係不得了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:15:50.000Z","msg":"馬面人"},{"pid":"d981d9fc08020a06f1f1d87bbb35b3ec9f68eb17","tid":1027024,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"咁樣識女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073bd48f923f123a49dc3a701c66d7ad87c1ef83","tid":1027024,"uid":175112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"塊面長撚到。。。"},{"pid":"7c9b935a6ed713fa2f6e2757e4893edcbabefac2","tid":1027024,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:22:07.000Z","msg":"係旺角撞過真人<br />\n好一般<br />\n係對波大"},{"pid":"1ee1b449cd9f48923a42195c220e883a795bb643","tid":1027024,"uid":137800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:22:26.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰"},{"pid":"c51e8f094ec13d5a2b7fff6896b99183c51b7ad2","tid":1027024,"uid":21398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:22:48.000Z","msg":"法官大人。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屌呀！<img src=\"/assets/f